OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy at first this morning
OL,6,Fwith a few spots of drizzle. However,
OL,7,Fcloud will gradually lift and break to
OL,8,Fgive some good sunny spells through
OL,9,Fthe day. Feeling warm in the sunshine.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FStaying dry tonight with
OL,12,Fclear spells. A warm night in the
OL,13,Fsouth of the region, but cooler in the
OL,14,Fnorth as temperatures dip into single
OL,15,Ffigures.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FA largely dry and bright day
OL,18,Fwith plenty of sunny spells. A small
OL,19,Fchance of a few light showers later in
OL,20,Fthe afternoon. Feeling hot and
OL,21,Fincreasingly humid.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
