OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:
OL,6,FIncreasingly hot and humid through the
OL,7,Fstart of next week with plenty of
OL,8,Fstrong sunshine. Mostly dry and just a
OL,9,Fsmall chance of a few showers.
